quran[357]{c,v,t}:
  36,28,Ne shikhweshiakhwo khubandu be imbeli wuwe omukanda kweliyie okhurula mwikulu ne shikhwali beshia tawe
  36,29,"Lwali butswa oluyoka lulala, mana bo nibanyisibwa"
  36,30,"Abaane, ebeelelela Abandu banje Omurumwa yesiyesi shiyabetselaga tawe okhula bamubayile"
  36,31,Koo shibalolangakhwo emikanda chinga chakhwasishia imbeli wabu. Abo toto shibalibakalushila tawe
  36,32,Ne toto boosi balikhung’asibwa barerwe imbeli wefu
  36,33,"Ne eshimanyisio khubo-liloba [eliuma] liafwa khulilamusinjia mana khuchesemwo imele yabaliitsanga"
  36,34,Ne nikhukasiamwo emikunda chie tsitende nende tsizabibu ne nikhukasiamwo tsisebele
  36,35,"Kho balie khubiamo bie nende ake emikhono chiabu chilakholele tawe, koo shibakhupanga orio tawe"
  36,36,"Oluyali nilwa Nyasaye waloonga eshisatsa\tneshikhasi\tbioosi khubimelanga mwiloba nende enywe abeene nende ebiabalamanyile tawe"
  36,37,"Ne eshilo neshimanyisio shindi khubo, olwa khurusinjiamwo eshiteere nabo baba mushiilima"
  36,38,Ne eliuba lichendanga khushichelo shalio esho nisho eshichelo shia Nyasaye Owamaani Omumanyi muno
  36,39,Ne Omwesi khwakukasilia ebichelo okhula okhukalukha shingala kwali shinga likhamari liumile
  36,40,Eliuba shiniliula khumwesi nohomba eshilo okhubura eshitere nabo biosi bibotokhananga khutsinjila tsiabio
  36,41,Ne ni eshimanyisio khubo mbu efwe khwachinga olwibulo lwabu musafina yetsula
  36,42,Ne nikhwabalonjela okhurula khwifwani eyo ebiabarakanga
  36,43,Ne nikhwenya nikhubayibisia ne abulaho ubakhoonya nohomba shibahabinwa tawe
  36,44,Halali tsimbabaasi tsirulanga khwifwe nende omwikhoyo kwebise bititi
  36,45,Ne nibaboolelwa mbu; “mwilinde nende khukali imbeli wenyu nende kali inyuma wenyu mwakhaba murio mwanyoola okhubeelwa tsimbabaasi.”
  36,46,Ne ishimanyisio shiosi shiosi shia Nyasaye wabu Omulesi nishiboolela shibabukulangamwo oluchendo tawe
  36,47,"Ne nibaboolelwa mbu; “rusie khubilia bia Nyasaye wenyu abakabile ,abakhayi baboolelenga Abasuubili mbu; ‘‘koo khubalisie biala ba Nyasaye niyenya nabalisia? toto enywe muli mubukori bwabulafu.”"
  36,48,Ne baboolanga mbu; “kamukhulakanga kano kalirulila lina nimuli toto abahabwene.”
  36,49,Shibalindanga halali oluyoka lulala butwsa lulibabukula nabo nibali mukhusolana
  36,50,Mana shibalinyoola okhulaamila nohomba shibalikalukha khubandu babu tawe
  36,51,Na olwa olwika lulikhupwa balirula mubilindwa nibelushila ewa Nyasaye wabu Omulesi
  36,52,"Baliboola mbu; “abayie! wina ukhulamusiyie\tolwakhubeele nikhukonele, kano niko kayalaka Omunji wetsimbabaasi ne Abarumwa baboola katoto.”"
  36,53,Ne shiluliba halali oluyoka lulala butwsa mana boosi balikhung’asibwa imbeli wefu
  36,54,"Mana olwa lelo abulaho yesiyesi olikholelwa\tamabii\tkosikosi ne shimulirungwa halali kalia kamwakholaga"
  36,55,Toto Abandu bo mwikulu lelo bali khumilimo nibakonele (khubusangafu)
  36,56,Bo nende abakhaye babu nibali mubinikha bayeshele khubisaala biobwokhola
  36,57,"Balinyolamwo tsimbia tsiosi tsiebiamo, nebalinyoolamwo buli eshiabeenya"
  36,58,"“Omulembe,” likhuwa lirula khu Nyasaye Omulesi Wobukoosia muno"
  36,59,Ne enywe abetsimbii mwiyawule olwalelo
  36,60,"Koo shindalakana ninanyu mbu enywe Abandu mulalaama Shetani tawe , toto ye ni Omusuku wenyu owabulafu"
  36,61,Ni mbu munaame esie ino niyo injila ingololofu
  36,62,"No khubwatoto ye yakosia omukanda omukhongo mwinywe , koo shimwaparangakhwo tawe"
  36,63,Mana ino niyo Jahanam yamwalakungwa
  36,64,Injilemwo lelo shingala mwakhayanga
  36,65,Olwa lelo khutimbia eminwa chiabu ne imikhono chiabu chiboole ninafu ne ibilenje biabu birusie obuloli khu kalia kabakholanga
  36,66,Ne khwenyanga khwakhatimbiyie tsimoni tsiabu baba nibashilanila injila halali bakhalutsi barie
  36,67,"Ne\tkhwenyanga khwakhabakalukhaniye ifwani abali hao butswa, mana shibakhanyalile okhutsia nohomba okhukalukha tawe"
  36,68,Ne wakhukofusia khumukalusinjia inyuma mubulonji mana koo shibakhaparangakhwo
  36,69,"Ne shikhwamwechesia [Muhammad] tsinyimbo tawe ne kano shikenyekhana khuye tawe, shino ni eshitsulisio nende Ikurani iretsanga abulafu"
  36,70,Khulwo khwikanyilisilia ushili omulamu ne likhuwa libure khubakhayi
  36,71,"Ko shibalolanga mbu khwabaloonjela okhurulana khumilimo chie mikhono chiefu tsisolo tsiemiruko, etsia barukanga"
  36,72,Ne nikhubanguyisilia etsindi mutsisolo etso tsiabaninangakhwo ne etsindi batsiliitsaanga
  36,73,Ne bo banyoolanga mutsisolo etso obukhonyi nende ebinywebwa kho mana shibakhupanga orio tawe
  36,74,Ne batila Abanyasaye bandi habundu wa Nyasaye mbu khobanyoole obukhoonyi
  36,75,Shibalinyala okhubakhonya halali abo nibo baliba Abasikari babu olwabali khwitsila
  36,76,"Manaamakhuwakabukalakhubelesia tawe, toto efwe khwamanya kabafisanga nende kabaretsaanga habulafu"
  36,77,Ne Omundu shalolanga mbu khwamuloonga okhurulana nende indonyande ya amatsi kolwibulo mana toto ye niye omuseeri wahabulafu
  36,78,"Ne alakhuchelasilia naye yebilila okhulongwa khukhwe -mana naboola mbu : “ ni wina oyo ulilamusia ebikumba nibimalile okhubulungukha?”"
  36,79,"Boola mbu; “ alibilamusia ulia wabiloonga olwokhuranjilila, naye ni Omumanyi muno wabuli okhuloonga khwosi”"
  36,80,Ulia wabakholela okhunyoola omulilo okhurula khumusala omubisi mana nimunyoola okhubwana omulilo okhurulana ninakwo
  36,81,Koo waloonga likulu nende eshialo shanyala okhulonga bafwana ninabo? Khulwa shina naye niye Omuloonji Omukhongo Owamachesi muno
  36,82,"Toto likhuwa lilie niyenya eshindu ashiboolela butswa mbu: “ ba’’ ni shiba"
  36,83,"Mana yatswenukha ulia wobwami bwa buli eshindu buli mumukhono kukwe, ne ewuwe niwo amulikalusibwa"
  37,1,Nditsuba khubemaanga khulunyaali
  37,2,Nende khubalia bakaninjia amabii
  37,3,Nende khubalia basoomanga obwitsulisio
  37,4,Toto Nyasaye wenyu nimulala butswa
  37,5,Nyasaye Omulesi welikulu nende eshialo nende ebili hakari wabio. Ne ni Nyasaye Omulesi we ebukwe tsiosi
  37,6,Toto efwe khwarona likulu liahambi khutsing’ining’ini
  37,7,Khulwokhulinda okhurulana nende buli Shetani Omukhayi
  37,8,"Balanyoola okhuwulila ebilonje bioluyali, ne baloondungwayo buli mumbeka"
  37,9,Baloondungwa ne bali nende eshinyasio shilawa
  37,10,"Halali ulia upusulanga eshindu eshititi , ne mana shimulondangakhwo eshikhupo shimesamesanga"
  37,11,Barebekhwo mbu koo abo ni baloongwa okhuloongwa okhutinyu muno okhushila ebilonje bindi biakhwaloonga? Toto efwe khwabaloonga okhurulana khuliloba litilanga
  37,12,Owukanga nabo bakholanga omubayo
  37,13,Ne nibetsulisibwa shibetsulilanga tawe
  37,14,Ne nibalola eshimanyisio nibakhola omubayo
  37,15,"Ne baboola mbu: “kano shinishiosi shiosi tawe halali ni obulosi butswa buli habulafu.”"
  37,16,"Mbunikhufwanikhumalileokhubaliloba nende ebikumba, kho toto khulilamusibwa"
  37,17,Kata bapapa befu bakhale
  37,18,"Boola mbu: “mmm! nanyu nimuli batutuyibwe .”"
  37,19,"Eyo oluyoka lulikhupwa lulala butswa, ni hawo niwo abalilola"
  37,20,"Baliboola mbu: “ abayiee, ino niyo inyanga yomurungo.”"
  37,21,Ino niyo inyanga yeyindukho yamwakhayanga
  37,22,Bakhung’asie boosi bakhola amabii nende abakhasi babu nende balia boosi babalaamanga
  37,23,Nibakhaya okhulaama Nyasaye bachomie khunjila yomulilo kwa Jahannam
  37,24,Mana mubeemie. Totobo balarebwa
  37,25,“Mubeele murie? Shichila shina nimulakhoonyana?”
  37,26,Halali olwalelo balaloonda lilako
  37,27,Balihengana abeene khubeene nibarebana
  37,28,"Baliboola mbu: “ toto enywe mwakhwitsilanga okhurula omukhono omulunji”"
  37,29,"Balibakalusia mbu: “Halali enywe abeene shimwali Abasuubili tawe.”"
  37,30,“Efwe shikhwali nobunyali khwinywe tawe halali enywe abeene mwali abakori”
  37,31,Mana omuse kwa Nyasaye wefu Omulesi kumalile okhubura. Toto efwe khulapila butswa eshinyasio
  37,32,Khwabakosia eshichila mbu fwesi khwali abakori
  37,33,Toto abo inyanga eyo balisaanga halala mushinyasio
  37,34,Endio nilwakhulikholela Abamabii
  37,35,"Olwa baboolelungwa mbu: “abulaho Nyasaye ulaamwa khubwatoto halali Nyasaye Mulala butswa- besuunganga"
  37,36,Baboolanga mbu efwe khuleshesa Abanyasaye befu okhubeela Omukaasi wetsinyimbo wuno Omulalu
  37,37,Halali ye yetsa khubwatoto ne afuchilisania nende Abarumwa
  37,38,Toto enywe mulipila eshinyasio eshilulu
  37,39,Ne shimulirungwa tawe halali kalia akamwakholanga
  37,40,Halali Abasumba ba Nyasaye abalobole
  37,41,Abo nibo balinyoola omukabo omubiishe
  37,42,"Ebiamo , nabo balihebwa oluyali"
  37,43,Mumikunda chobwokholo
  37,44,Baliba khubisaala nibahengane
  37,45,Balibotokhanilibwa eshisanda shieshinywebwa shieyisebele
  37,46,"Eshinywebwa eshilafu , eshimilimili khu ushinywa"
  37,47,"Shibula obubii , nohomba shishibameesia tawe"
  37,48,Ne baliba nende Abakhasi betsimoni tsietsisoni tsindayi
  37,49,Abakhasi shinga amabuyu kaliindwa
  37,50,"Baliinjila bachake , okhureebana abeene khubeene"
  37,51,"Aliboola omubooli mulala mubo: “toto esie ndali nende Omwitsa.”"
  37,52,"Yambolelanga mbu: “lano ewe ulimubafuchililanga?”"
  37,53,"‘‘Mbu nikhufwa khwaba liloba nende ebikumba, mbu khulirungwa mana khwabalwa?’’"
  37,54,"Aliboola mbu: “ laano enywe mulola murie?”"
  37,55,Mana alimuhenga kho alimulola hakari wa Jahannam
  37,56,"Aliboola mbu: “wallahi, Nyasaye mulala wali ahambi okhungosia.”"
  37,57,Tsikhayanga okhuba tsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye wanje omulesi ndakhabeele mubalia abenjisibwamwo
  37,58,Koo! Efwe shikhulifwa tawe
  37,59,"Halali okhufwa khwefu khwokhuranga, nafu shikhulinyoola eshinyasio tawe"
  37,60,"Toto\tkhuno\tnikho\tokhubura okhukhongo"
  37,61,"Ne\tshinga kano, nikabakhole balia bakhola"
  37,62,Koo okhubukanilwa endi shinokhulayi nohomba omusaala kwa Zaquum
  37,63,Toto efwe khwakukhola okhuba eshinyasio khubalia abamabii
  37,64,Toto oko ni omusaala kurulanga hakari wa Jahannamu
  37,65,Ebibuli bie biamo biakwo bili shinga omurwe kwa mashetani
  37,66,Toto abo balilia ebiamo ebo mana betsusie tsinda tsiabu
  37,67,Mana khu ako belesibwe amaatsi kayile karabachila
  37,68,Mana obwatoto amakalushilo kabu kaliba Jahannam
  37,69,Toto bo banyoola Basabwe nibakora
  37,70,Nabo nibakhola lwangu okhuloonda amaseenelo kabu
  37,71,Ne khubwatoto bamala okhukora imbeli wabu Abandu bakhale abaanji
  37,72,Ne toto efwe khwabarumila abekanyilisi
  37,73,Mana henga olole shingala indukho yabalia ebekanyilisibwa
  37,74,Halali Abasumba ba Nyasaye abalobole
  37,75,"Ne toto Nuhu Yakhulaanga , ne efwe khuli abalayi po abafuchililanga"
  37,76,Ne nikhumuhabina ye halala nende Abandu be okhurulana nende amasila amakhongo
  37,77,Mana nikhukhola olwibulo lulwe okhutoong’a
  37,78,Mana nikhulekha ifuma indayi khubetsa inyuma wuwe
  37,79,Omuleembe kube khu Nuhu mushialo shioosi
  37,80,Toto endio nilwakhurunganga abakholi bamalayi
  37,81,Toto ye ali Mubasumba befu Abasuubili
  37,82,Mana Abandi abo nikhubasishia mumatsi
  37,83,Ne toto Ibrahim yali mumukaanda kukwe
  37,84,Olwa yetsela Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi nende Omwoyo kukwe kwoosi
  37,85,"Olwa yaboolela Papa wuwe nende Abandu bebe mbu: “nishina shiamulamaanga?”"
  37,86,Eminyasaye chiobubeyi echilali Nyasaye nichiamwenyanga?”
  37,87,‘‘Mupariranga shina Nyasaye Omulesi webilonje bioosi?”
  37,88,Mana nasitia tsimoni okhuhenga tsing’ining’ini
  37,89,"Naboola mbu: “toto esie endwala.”"
  37,90,Nabo nibamulekha nibamufutarira omukongo
  37,91,"Mana nabwondela Eminyasaye chiabu. Nachiboolela mbu: “shichila shina nimulaliitsanga?’’"
  37,92,‘‘Mubeele murie amulalomalomanga tawe?’’
  37,93,Mana nachikalukhanila nachikhupa nomukhono omulunji
  37,94,Mana nibamwitsila lwangu lwangu
  37,95,"Naboola mbu: “ enywe mulaamanga ebindu bia mwiraanyanga abeene?”"
  37,96,Ne Nyasaye niye wabaloonga halala nende akamukholanga ako
  37,97,Nenibaboola mbu mumumbashile eshiumbashe mana mumusukune mumulilo
  37,98,Benya okhumukholela amabii halali nikhubakhola bo okhuba bahasi
  37,99,"Ne naboola mbu : “ toto esie ewuya enzia ewa Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, ye alalunjisia”"
  37,100,"Ewe Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, mbelesie ulia uli mubakholi bamalayi"
  37,101,Mana nikhumusubisia Omwana Omwihotselefu
  37,102,"Olwa yoola eshichelo shiokhuchenda ninaye yamuboolela mbu: “ewe mwana wanje , toto esie endutsi mumaloro mbu ekhusinzanga, kho hengamwo olola orie?” naboola mbu: “ ewe papa wanje, khola shinga olomesibungwa witsa okhunyoola Nyasaye nachama nendi mubalia befwiila”"
  37,103,"Kho boosi babili olwa behotselesia , mana namukonelia obweni"
  37,104,"Nikhumulanga mbu : “ewe Ibrahim!”"
  37,105,"Omalileokhukholahabwenikhumaloro ako, toto endio nilwakhurunganga Abakholi bamalayi"
  37,106,Toto kano ni amatemo kali habulafu
  37,107,Mana nikhumuhelesia eshisinzo shioluyali
  37,108,Mana nikhuleshela ifuma indayi khubetsa inyuma
  37,109,Omulembe kube khu Ibrahim
  37,110,Endio nilwakhurunganga Abakholi bamalayi
  37,111,Toto ye ali Mubandu befu basuubila
  37,112,"Ne nikhumusuubisia okhwibulwa khwa Is’haaq, naye ni Omurumwa womubandu Abalayi"
  37,113,Mana nikhumuhelesia tsimbabaasi ye nende Is’haaq. Ne mulwibulo lwabu nibarulamwo Abandu abalayi nende balia bakhola amabii khumioyo chiabu habulafu
  37,114,Netoto khwakholela obulayi Musa nende Harun
  37,115,Nikhumuhabina halala nende Abandu babu okhurulana nende obutinyu obukhongo
  37,116,Mana nikhubahabina nibaba nibo abashila
  37,117,Ne nikhuhelesia babili abo eshitabu shinoosinjia
  37,118,"Mana\tnikhubalunjisia\tkhunjila ingololofu"
  37,119,Mana nikhubaleshela ifuma indayi khubalia betsa inyuma wabu
  37,120,Omulembe kube khu Musa nende Harun
  37,121,Toto endio nilwakhurunganga balia abalayi
  37,122,Toto babili abo bali Mubasumba befu abalayi
  37,123,Ne toto Elyas yali Mubarumwa
  37,124,"Olwa yaboolela Abandu bebe mbu: “shimuritsanga tawe?”"
  37,125,Mulaamanga Baal ( eshimoosi shieidhahabu) ne mulekha omuloonji mwene
  37,126,Nyasaye Omulesi wenyu nende wa bapapa benyu bakhale
  37,127,Mana nibamuyingasia. Ne toto balikhung’asibwa (mumulilo)
  37,128,"Halali\tAbasumba\tba\tNyasaye Abatswunulwa"
  37,129,Mana nikhubaleshela ifuma indayi khubalia betsa inyuma wabu
  37,130,Omulembe kube khu Ilyas
  37,131,Toto endio nilwakhurunganga balia Abalayi
  37,132,Toto ye ali Mubasumba befu Abasuubila
  37,133,Ne toto Luti ali Mubarumwa
  37,134,Olwa khwamuhabina halala nende Abandu baye boosi
  37,135,Halali Omukhasi omushiele owali mubatong’a inyuma
  37,136,Mana nikhusishia abandi abo
  37,137,Ne toto enywe mubaburangakhwo mumabwibwi
  37,138,"Nende\teshilo,\tmana\tkho shimukharetsangakhwo mubwongo tawe"
  37,139,Ne toto Yunus yali mulala khubarumwa
  37,140,Olwa yelushila muliaro litsule
  37,141,"Mana nibasanjilana mumakhuwa, mana nikamukwiila"
  37,142,Mana inyeni nimumila naye nali ufunaanibwa
  37,143,Ne akhayanga okhuba mubalia abetsoominjia Nyasaye
  37,144,Yakhamenyele munda mwayo okhuula inyanga yokhulamusibwa mubafu
  37,145,"Mana nikhumusukuna khulukuku, naye nali omulwale"
  37,146,Nenikhumumesilia omumela kwelihondo
  37,147,Ne khwamuruma khubandu iyelefu imia ndala nohomba bashilaho awo
  37,148,Mana nibasuubila nenikhubara mubwokholo okhula okhufwa khwabu
  37,149,"Ne bareebe mbu: “ Nyasaye wuwo niye uli nende Abana abakhana nabo babe nende Abana abasiani"
  37,150,Nohomba khwaloonga Abamalaika okhuba beshikhasi nabo nibalola
  37,151,Ne toto manya mbu khububeyi bwabu baboolanga mbu
  37,152,“Nyasaye yebula” ne toto obo ni obubeyi
  37,153,"Oh, yalobola Abana beshikhana okhushila beshisiani"
  37,154,Baane mulimurie? Mubusinjia murie
  37,155,Ohh shimuparangakhwo tawe
  37,156,Nohomba muli nende eshifune shiatoto
  37,157,Mana nakharerekhwo eshitabu shienyu (itaurati) nikali mbu muboolanga obwatoto
  37,158,"Ne baraho okhwinjilana khwolwikho hakari waye nende Amajini, ne Amajini kamala okhumanya mbu toto (baboolanga bario) balikhung’asibwa (mumililo)"
  37,159,"Oluyali ni lwa Nyasaye , Nyasaye\tnomutswenufu\tmuno khukabamuchishilanga"
  37,160,Halali Abasumba ba Nyasaye Abatswenufu
  37,161,Mana enywe nende abamulamanga
  37,162,Shimunyala okhubakosia tawe
  37,163,Halali ulia ulinjila mumulilo
  37,164,Ne habulaho yesiyesi mwifwe halali alinende habundu wuwe amanyikhane
  37,165,Ne toto efwe nefwe khwemaanga olunyaali
  37,166,Ne toto nefwe betsoominjia
  37,167,Ne baliho balia baboolanga mbu
  37,168,‘‘Khubeetsangakhwo nende ametsulisio ka Abandu bakhale (bebitabu)
  37,169,Toto khwakhabeele Abasumba ba Nyasaye Abatswenufu.’’
  37,170,"Halali\t(olwashitabu\tshiabetsela) bashikhaya mana hambi hano nibalole"
  37,171,Ne toto likhuwa liefu liamala okhuranjilila khubasumba befu Abarumwa
  37,172,Mbu abo toto nibo balihabinwa
  37,173,Ne omukanda kwefu kwabalwani niko kulishila
  37,174,Kho baleshe butswa khubise ebititi
  37,175,"Ne bahenje butswa, ahambi hano balitsa okhumanya"
  37,176,Koo eshinyasio shia Nyasaye nishio shiabayungubasinjia
  37,177,"Kho eshinyasio olwashilibeshela mushikuri, iliba itsuli imbi khubalia bekanyilisibwa"
  37,178,Kho baleshesa khubise bititi
  37,179,Ne bahenje butswa nabo balitsa okhumanya
  37,180,Nyasaye Omulesi nomutswenufu muno okhurulana khukabamuchishilanga
  37,181,Ne omulembe kube Khubarumwa
  37,182,Ne oluyali lwoosi nilwa Nyasaye Omulesi wabiloonje bioosi
  38,1,Swad. Nditsuba khu Ikurani eyili nende ametsulisio
  38,2,Halali Abakhayi bali mwikhwilola nende obuyingani
  38,3,"Ni emikanda chinga chiakhwasishia imbeli wabu niboopa obuyoka , ne ebise biokhuwonibwa biali biburire"
  38,4,"Ne bawuka mbu Omwikanyilisi okhurula mubo okhubetsela , mana nibaboola mbu: “uno ni Omulosi Omubeyi.”"
  38,5,Eh! akholele Abanyasaye okhuba Nyasaye mulala yenyene! Toto kano ni amakhuwa khokhuchenyia
  38,6,"Mana Abakhongo babu nibarula nibababoolela mbu: “mutsie mana mutinyesa Khubanyasaye benyu, toto endio nilwakenyekhana.”"
  38,7,"Efwe shikhwawulilakhwo kano mushima shiefu shiokhumalilikha tawe, ne kano shineshindu tawe halali ni obuchishi butswa"
  38,8,"Mbu niye butswa weshilibwa amekanyilisio mwifwe. Halali abo bali nende eshibeyibeyi khu amekanyilisio kanje, ne mana bashili okhupila eshinyasio shianje"
  38,9,"Nohomba bali nende ebiachi bietsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi, Owa amani Khakaba"
  38,10,Nohomba bo bali nende obwami bwomwikulu nende khushialo nende ebili hakari wabio? Khomana banine tsinjila tsiokhutsia eyo
  38,11,Oko niko omukanda kwabalwani kulishilwa mumikanda chilia chilishilwa
  38,12,"Bayingana inyuma wabu Abandu ba Nuhu, nende babu A’di nende Firaun owali nende ebiumbashe"
  38,13,Nende Thamud nende Abandu ba Luti nende Abandu bomumutsuru. Echo nichio emikanda
  38,14,Abo boosi bayingasia Abarumwa mana nibakhoyeshela eshinyasio
  38,15,Ne bano shiabalindangasa ni oluyoka lulala butswa olulali ehale tawe
  38,16,"Nabo baboolanga mbu: “Nyasaye wefu Omulesi khurerere eshinyasio shiefu inyanga yeyindukho nishili okhuula.”"
  38,17,"Wisumilisie khukababoolanga ako, ne witsulile Omusumba wefu Daudi Owa amani. Toto ye yali omunji wokhusaba eshileshelo"
  38,18,Netoto khwahotselesia ebikulu halala ninaye nibitsoomia ingolobe nende mumabwibwi halala ninaye
  38,19,"Ne kata amayoni kakhung’asibwa emikanda nemikanda, koosi kali amehotselefu khuye"
  38,20,"Ne nikhumeta amani obwami bubwe, ne nikhumuwa amachesi nende obumanyi bwokhubusia omuse"
  38,21,Ne koo wawulikhwo olukano lwabasoolani olwa bekalilwa okhwinjila munzu
  38,22,"Olwa benjila wa Daudi , naye nabaria, nibaboola mbu: “olaria tawe, efwe khuli abasoolani babili, mulala wefu akosele owashie, mana okhukabukhasie khubwatoto , ne olakwila elubeka tawe, ne okhulunjisie khunjila yo bwatoto"
  38,23,"Toto uno ni Omusiani wefu, ali nende amakondi amakhasi amakhumi tisa nende tisa, nasi endisa nende likondi lilalasa lieshikhasi, mana aboolanga mbu :“mbelesie elilio elo ekhuruchile” (nasi shindenya tawe) ne yashilile khumakhuwa"
  38,24,"Toto ye akholele obubii okhusaba likondi lilio okhumeta khukeke, netoto abeyisanga abanji bakholelanga obubii khubeene, halali balia basuubila mana nibakhola amalayi nenibatiti mubo. Mana Daudi nalola mbu khumukholeele amatemo, nasaba eshileshelo khu Nyasaye wuwe, mana nakwa hasi okhwihotselesia khu Nyasaye wuwe nende okhumukalushila"
  38,25,"Mana nikhumuleshela ako, netoto ye alinende eshisaala eshikhongo nende habundu halayi alikalukha khwifwe"
  38,26,"Ewe Daudi toto efwe khwakhukhola okhuba omulindi wefu khushialo, kho khalaka emise chia Abandu khubwatoto ne olalonda obwikombi bwomwoyo bwakhukosia khunjila ya Nyasaye , toto balia balekha injila ya Nyasaye abo balinyoola eshinyasio eshilulu khulwa okhubula oluchendo khwabu muyinyanga yokhubalilwa"
  38,27,Ne shiwalonga likulu nende eshialo nende ebili hakari wabio eshikhaya tawe. Ako ni amaparo kabakhayi. Bali nende eshinyasio eshilulu Abakhayi abo mumulilo kubalinyoola
  38,28,"Nohomba khukhole balia basubila babe shinga balia bakholanga amabii khushialo, nohomba khukhole abaria Nyasaye shinga abetsimbii"
  38,29,"Eshitabu shino shakhwakhwishilia ewe shilimwo tsimbabaasi tsinyinji, kho banyoole okhupaara mutsinyaali tsiashio, ne bobwoongo banyoole okhuwulila"
  38,30,"Ne khwahelesia Dawudi Suleiman yali Omusumba omulayi muno, toto ye yali omunji wokhukalushila Nyasaye"
  38,31,"Olwa yarumilwa ingolobe tsifarasi tsiwulelanga nitsiemele,\ttsinyangu okhutsunukha"
  38,32,"Mana naboola mbu : “esie ndachama ebindu ebilayi khulwa okhwitsulila Nyasaye wanje, mana (tsifarasi etso) nitsifisa inyuma weshikalilo. (Suleiman niyenya mbu atsilole khandi)"
  38,33,"Mutsikalusie khwisie , mana nachaka okhutsitilakhwo mwikosi nende khubilenje"
  38,34,"Mana nikhura Suleiman mumatemo, nenikhura omubili khushisaala shishie, mana nakalukha okhusaba eshileshelo"
  38,35,"Naboola mbu: “Nyasaye wanje undeshele ne umbelesie obwaami bwo mundu wundi alalinyoola inyuma wanje tawe, toto ewe newe Omuwani.’’"
  38,36,"Mana nikhukhola omuyeka okhumurumushila,\tkwachendanga khumunwa kukwe, hosi hosi ayenya okhuula"
  38,37,"Mana nikhukhola amashetani okhumurumushila, koosi kombakhanga nende keyibilanga"
  38,38,Nende abaandi boboyungwa khuminyororo
  38,39,"Shino ni eshihanwa shiefu, kho mana rusia nohomba shitiile, shibula eshichelo"
  38,40,"Ne toto ye ali nende oluyali okhwinjisibwa ewefu, nende habundu halayi muno wokhukalukha"
  38,41,"Ne yitsulila Omusumba wefu Ayub, olwa yalanga Nyasaye wuwe mbu: “ toto esie shetani yanderere obusinyifu nende obusandi.”"
  38,42,"Nyasaye namuboolela mbu : “sieba hasi eshilenje shishio (isebele nirundukha hasi awo) kho amatsi amanyifu ko khwisinga wisinje ngako, nende kokhunywa onywe.”"
  38,43,"Mana nikhumuhelesia Abandu bebe nende abandi shinga abo, nende tsimbabaasi tsirula khwifwe, nende eshitsulisio khubaandu bobwongo"
  38,44,"Ne bukula mumukhono kukwo olusaala , omukhupile (omukhaye wuwo khulwokhwitsuba khwa wetsuba- khumabii kayakhola) ne olafunaka eshitsubo tawe. Toto kwamunyoola nali Omwifwiili Omusumba Omulayi, toto yali Omwisumilisi muno"
  38,45,Ne yitsulila Omusumba wefu Ibrahim nende Is’haaq nende Yaqub bali ba amaani nende amachesi
  38,46,Toto efwe khwabalobola khulikhuwa lilayi muno liokhwitsulila mwikulu
  38,47,Ne toto abo bali khwifwe Mubandu abalobole abalayi
  38,48,Ne yitsulila Ismail nende Alyasa nende dhil kifli ne abo boosi bali Mubandu abalayi
  38,49,Kano ni ametsulisio ne toto bwene balia baria Nyasaye habundu wabu wokhukalukha aliba alayi muno
  38,50,"Emikunda chomwikulu echilaliwa, chilikulwa emiliango shichila bo"
  38,51,Omo baliyiekhamwo nibalaanga ebiamo ebinji nende ebinywebwa ebilayi po
  38,52,"Ne baliba nabakhaye babu abasangasia tsimoni , abolubaka lulala"
  38,53,"Kano niko kamwalakwa [okhunyoola] inyanga yokhubalwa"
  38,54,Toto kuno niko umukabo kwefu okulawetsaanga tawe
  38,55,Endio nilwakaliba netoto balia baruumanga olwakho amakalushilo kabu kaliba amabii
  38,56,"Jahannam balinjilamwo, nabo ni obukono obubii muno bwakhukonakhwo"
  38,57,Endio nilwakaliba mana banywemwo amatsi komulilo nende kamafila
  38,58,Nende ebinyasio bindi ngabino ebinji
  38,59,"Kuno niko omukanda kulinjila halala ninanyu, balibula okhwinjisibwa obulayi, toto abo balinjila mumulilo"
  38,60,"Baliboola mbu : “enywe nenywe mubula amwinjila halayi, nenywe mwachila nikhunyoola eshinyasio, kho muli Abandu ababii muno.”"
  38,61,"Baliboola mbu: “ Nyasaye wefu balia bachila nikhunyoola kano bameete eshinyasio mara khabili mumulilo. “"
  38,62,"Mana ababii balia balireeba mbu: “kabeele karie akhulalolanga Abandu bakhwabalilanga mubabii mumulilo kuno?”"
  38,63,Koo khwababayila nohomba tsimoni tsiefu nitsilalolanga
  38,64,Toto kano okhusolana khuno khwa Abandu bomumuliro nitoto
  38,65,"Boola mbu: “esie endisa Omwikanyilisi, ne abulaho Nyasaye wundi owulali Nyasaye mulala Owamani muno. ”"
  38,66,"Nyasaye welikulu nende eshialo nende bili hakari wabio Owamaani muno, Omunji weshileshelo"
  38,67,Boola kano ni amacheni amakhongo muno aka enywe mukhayanga
  38,68,"Ka enywe mubula ninako oluchendo. [enywe nanyu mukakhayanga]"
  38,69,Shindali nende obumanyi kebilonje ebikhongo bioluyali olwabiayingananga
  38,70,Ndahebwa obufimbuli shichila esie endi Omwikanyilisi Owabulafu
  38,71,"Olwa Nyasaye wuwo yaboolela Abamalaika mbu: “esie enonjele Omundu okhurula khuliloba.”"
  38,72,Kho olwandalamukasia mana emufuramwo omwoyo okhurulana ninasi kho mumwinamile khukhumuwulila
  38,73,Abamalaika boosi nibeenama- halala
  38,74,Halali Iblisi yaba Omufuru mana naba mubakhayi
  38,75,"Nyasaye namureeba mbu ; “Ewe Iblis shina shikhukayiile okhwinamila khushienonjele nende emikhono chianje, ofurire nohomba oli mubakhongo?”"
  38,76,"Shetani naboola ‘Esie endi omulayi okhumushila ye, waloonga esie okhurulana khu muliro naye nomulonga okhurula khuliloba.”"
  38,77,"Nyasaye namuboolela mbu: “’mana rula muno ewe oli neshitsubo.”"
  38,78,Ne eshitsubo shianje shikhulikhwo okhula inyanga yomurungo
  38,79,"Iblis naboola: ‘Nyasaye wanje mbelesie obwiyangu ndalafwa tawe okhula inyanga yokhulamusibwa mubafu"
  38,80,Nyasaye namuboolela; ‘‘mana ekhuhelesiyie obwiyangu.’’
  38,81,Okhula khubise bieyinyanga imanyishe
  38,82,"Iblis naboola mbu: ‘‘nditsuba khumaani koko toto nditsa okhukosia boosi [Abana ba Adam]”"
  38,83,Halali Abasumba bobo abatswenufu mubo
  38,84,"Nyasaye naboola mbu “Toto, ne emboola obwatoto"
  38,85,Ndiliitsusia Jahanam khu ewe nende balia boosi balikhuloonda mubo.”
  38,86,Boola mbu “ esie shebareba omurungo kwosikwosi tawe nohomba esie shendi omunichilisia tawe
  38,87,Kano ni ametsulisio butswa Khubandu
  38,88,Ne toto mulamanya amacheni kaye ahambi hano
  39,1,Okhwishibwa khweshitabu shino khurulana nende Nyasaye Owamani Owamachesi muno
  39,2,"Toto efwe khwakhwishilia eshitabu shino khubwatoto, kho mulaame Nyasaye yenyene mubutswenufu khu Dini yiyie butswa"
  39,3,"Toto Idini yabwene ni ya Nyasaye butswa, ne balia abeliindanga khu ulali Nyasaye nibaboola mbu: “ shikhubalamaanga tawe halali bakhusitie ahambi nende Nyasaye,” toto Nyasaye alibakabula khu kalia akabawukhananga. Toto Nyasaye shaluunjisinjia omubeeyi omukhayi tawe"
  39,4,"Nyasaye yenyanga okhuba nende Omwana yakhaloboole mubiloonje bibie owayenya, oluyali ni olulwe, niye Nyasaye mulala ukholanga liayenya"
  39,5,"Yaloonga likulu nende eshialo khubwatoto, ufuunikhanga eshiloo khushiteere, nende eshiteere khushiloo, mana nakhola eliuba nende omwesi mubiikhonyele , bioosi bichendanga khubise biarebwaho, manye mbu niye Owa amani Omulesheli muno"
  39,6,"Yaloonga okhurula Khumundu mulala, mana namurusiamwo owashie, mana nabarerera ebiruche ebisatsa nende ebikhasi tsimbia munane, abaloonganga mutsinda tsia banyinenywe oshiloonje okhutsia khushindi, mubiilima bitaru. Oyo niye Nyasaye Omulesi wenyu, obwami nobubwe, abulaho Nyasaye wundi owulali ye tawe, kho nanyu mulinjibungwa heena"
  39,7,"Ni mukhaya toto Nyasaye ni omuyinda khwinywe, ne shachamilanga Abasumba bebe obukhayi tawe, ne nimumwitsoomia alabafuchilila ne Omundu shalichinga obusiro bwo owashie tawe, mana mulikalukha ewa Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi, ne alibaboolela akamwakholanga toto ye ni Omumanyi muno khukali mubilifi"
  39,8,"Ne Omundu nanyoola amasila kosikosi asaba Nyasaye wuwe namukalushila, ne namuhelesia tsimbabaasi okhurula ewuwe yebilila akayasabanga imbeli mana natsokasia Nyasaye nende Abanyasaye bandi mbu kho akosie Abandu khu injila yiye, wikhoye nende obukhayi bubwo hatiti, toto ewe oli mubaandu bomumulilo"
  39,9,"Koo ulia ulaamanga eshilo Nyasaye wuwe niyeema niyenama mana naba noburi khu inyanga imalilishi, ne nasuubila okhunyoola tsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye wuwe. Boola mbu:“ bakhaba nashilala abamanyile nende abalamanyile tawe, toto abachesi nibobetsulilanga.’’"
  39,10,"Boola enywe Abasumba banje basuubila, murie Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi, balia bakhola amalayi khushialo khuno balinyoola amalayi, ne eshialo shia Nyasaye neshiyaangufu, toto abesumilisi balihebwa omurungo kwabu okhubura eshichelo"
  39,11,"Boola mbu: “esie ndalomesibwa okhulaama Nyasaye mubutswenufu"
  39,12,Ne ndalomesibwa okhuba weyimbeli mubasalamu
  39,13,"Boola mbu: “ esie eritsaanga eshinyasio shie inyanga ikhongo nekhaya okhuloonda ka Nyasaye Omulesi wanje.”"
  39,14,Ni Nyasaye butswa wenaamanga nemutswenushila
  39,15,"Kho lame shia mwenya owulali Ye. Boola mbu: “toto balia abatiba mana nibatibia emioyo chiabu inyanga yeyindukho,” koo manye mbu, okho nikho okhutiba khwa habulafu"
  39,16,"Baliba nende ebichelo biomulilo biawukhane hekulu nende hasi wabu, endio nilwa Nyasaye arisia Abandu bebe, enywe abasumba banje muurie"
  39,17,"Ne balia basita ehale khubulaami bwobukori mana nibamukalushila Nyasaye, basuubisibwa obulayi imbeli wa Nyasaye , subisia Abasumba banje"
  39,18,"Balia bawulilanga likhuwa mana nibaloonda lilia lilayi lialio, abo nibo ba Nyasaye yalunjisia, ne abo nibo bamachesi"
  39,19,"Ne ulia okhoyeshele okhunyoola omurungo kweshinyasio, ewe olinobunyali bwokhuhabina uli mumulilo"
  39,20,"Halali balia baria Nyasaye wabu balinyoola tsigorofa ebikoro biombakhwa hekulu webindi, emialo chiburanga hasi wabio, indache ya Nyasaye ne Nyasaye shanyala okhwima shiayakhulaka tawe"
  39,21,"Koo shololangakhwo shinga Nyasaye yeshinjia amaatsi okhurula mwikulu, mana nakabusia mutsindoto mwiloba, mana namesilia emimela chikabukhane obukondo, mana chiume chikalukhane chibe namabuyu, mana achikhole amasakaria , toto mu ako khulimwo nende eshitsulisio khubandu bamachesi"
  39,22,"Koo ulia wa Nyasaye yafungula eshilifu shishie khubuisilamu, mana naba mubulafu bururulanga ewa Nyasaye Omulesi ( bakhaba nashilala nende ulia womwoyo omumu?) eshinyasio eshikhongo shili khubemioyo emiumu chaletsulilanga Nyasaye, abo bali mubukori obwa habulafu"
  39,23,"Nyasaye yeshia amakhuwa amalayi muno , eshitabu shietsinyaali tsifwanana tsiakalushilwa, tsirenjinjia emibili chia balia abaria Nyasaye wabu Omulesi, mana nitsikololosia emibili chiabu nende emioyo chiabu khukhwitsulila Nyasaye, obo nibo obulunjifu bwa Nyasaye alunjisinjia khubwo owayenya, ne owa Nyasaye alekha abulaho umulunjisia"
  39,24,"Koo ulia wo bweni bubwe bulibukanana nende eshinyasio eshibii inyanga yeyindukho (aliba nashilala nende abalayi?) mana ababii baliboolelwa mbu: “ pile kalia kamwakholanga.”"
  39,25,Bakhaya balia abali imbeli wabu mana eshinyasio nishibetsela munjila yabalamanyile tawe
  39,26,"Mana Nyasaye nabakhofia eshinyasio shiobuteshele, ne eshinyasio shieyinyanga yeyindukho neshikhongo muno, bamanyanga khwo"
  39,27,Ne toto khwachelasilia Abandu mu Kurani ino buli imbia yamachelasio kho banyoole okhwitsulila
  39,28,Ikurani yolwarabu ibulamwo tsingatsio khobanyoole okhuria Nyasaye
  39,29,"Nyasaye achelasia Omundu uli nende Abaami bakholelanga halala basolananga, nende Omundu uli nende Omwami mulala, koo bakhaba nashilala? Oluyali lwoosi nilwa Nyasaye, halali obunji bwabu shibamanyile tawe"
  39,30,Toto ewe olifwa nabo boosi balifwa
  39,31,"Mana toto enywe imbeli wa Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi mulisoolana, inyanga yeyindukho"